# data_io_nbdev

The data_io_nbdev package is a python package that provides io interface
for the time sequence processing.

It consists of the following subpackages:

- dataflow
- pool
- buffer
- eos_struct
- utils
- conn
- config

## Install

``` sh
pip install data_io_nbdev
```
